description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'BEGINNER WORKOUT IN BED | lose weight at home' from the channel Dayana Wang.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Lose weight at home with this 10 minute beginners friendly body workout in bed! Make sure that you eat well and drink plenty of water to get fast results.
